1. Project Overview

This project is a Kids Learning Platform with:

Reading books

Practice homework (2-letter, 3-letter words, math)

Assignments

Class management

Student dashboard

Teacher dashboard

Marking system

NestJS backend + MongoDB

Next.js frontend (Vercel deploy)

All code must be written in TypeScript.

2. Technology Rules
Frontend

Use Next.js App Router.

Use Shadcn UI for components.

Use Tailwind CSS.

Use React Hook Form for forms.

Use Zustand or Context for state management.

Store API URL in NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL.

Backend

Use NestJS.

Use Mongoose for MongoDB schemas.

Use JWT Auth.

Implement role-based access:

admin

teacher

student

parent

Database

Use MongoDB Atlas.

Every collection must include:

createdAt

updatedAt

createdBy

